Switzerland to Respond to OECD Banking Critiques, Temps Says

-- B y   T o m   M u l i e r
-- 
2011-02-12T11:06:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-12/switzerland-to-respond-to-oecd-banking-critiques-temps-says.html
The Swiss government will soon
respond to the Organization for Economic Cooperation and
Development’s critiques on how it implemented new bank secrecy
rules in agreements with other countries,  Le Temps  said, citing
an unidentified person familiar with the situation.  The government will comment Feb. 14, Le Temps said, adding
that  Switzerland ’s  Finance Ministry  declined to comment to the
newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tom Mulier in Geneva at 
 tmulier@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at 
 cperri@bloomberg.net . 